title: Silky Van Gogh Le Iris Scarf
description:
Inspired by Vincent Van Gogh’s Iris collection, this silk scarf will make a great addition to your closet and accessory box. This timeless and trendy scarf will be beautiful around your neck, wrist, and handbag. Wrap around your favorite watch band to give that old watch a new look.

Details:

• 100% Silk

• Made in France

• 2.75x 40 inches
